      "message": "Can you elaborate on the sequence of events that yield a leak? `MCTPDDevice` drops its reference to the endpoint on the endpoint\u0027s `InterfacesRemoved` event from `mctpd` (breaking the cycle). `mctpd` the interface will be removed either because `.Remove` was called, or as a consequence of `.Recover` failing.\n\nHowever, there\u0027s also the possibility that `mctpd` stops or crashes. That looks to lead to a `NameOwnerChanged` event _but not_ an `InterfacesRemoved` event, might cause some trouble. Are you observing that? Or something else?",
